Y '''Nikola Tesla''' ([[Serbian language|Serbian]]: Никола Тесла) ([[Juliu 10]] [[1856]] - [[Eneru 7]] [[1943]]<ref>http://www.neuronet.pitt.edu/~bogdan/tesla/</ref>) metung yang bantug mabilug a yatu a [[Serbian American]] [[maninbentu]], [[physicist]], [[mechanical engineer]] at [[electrical engineer]]. Kebaluan ya keng kayang maka-aklasang gawa king dakal a miyayaliwang dispilina ning [[electrisidad at balani]] inyang pang19 at bayung  [[pang20 a dlianwa]]. Deng [[List of Tesla patents|patentadu nang Tesla's]] at obra theoretical ilang memuu keng makabayung pangatatag ning [[alternating current]] [[electric power]] (AC) systema, kayabe na ing [[polyphase system|polyphase]] [[power distribution]] systema at ing [[Electric motor#AC motors|AC motor]], nung nu minusbung ing  [[Kaduang Industrial Revolution]].

